id: pm-hj9h
title: "pm install should accept multiple package targets (help already advertises [targets...])"
description: "2026-07-06 audit #12 sandbox: pm install pm-a pm-b errors 'Install accepts one package source at a time' although help/usage shows install [options] [targets...]. Either loop installs over each target sequentially (preferred agent UX, saves N-1 process spawns) or fix the advertised signature. Wildcard '*' already batch-installs bundled packages, so batch semantics exist."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[3]: agent-ux,audit-followup,extensions
