author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "pm install a b c installs all three (per-target result rows, partial-failure reporting) or usage/help no longer advertises variadic targets; spec covers multi-target path."
parent: pm-ugqx
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: fixed
expected_result: pm install accepts multiple explicit targets and reports per-target success or failure without losing wildcard install behavior.
actual_result: "Multi-target install now runs targets sequentially, emits aggregate JSON rows with installed/failed counts, preserves wildcard collapse, and sets a failure exit code when any target fails."
